The '''2013 BRICS summit''' will be the fifth annual [[BRICS#BRICS summits|BRICS summit]], an international relations conference attended by the head of states or heads of government of the five member states [[Brazil]], [[Russia]], [[India]], [[China]] and [[South Africa]]. The summit will be held in South Africa in 2013.<ref>http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/brics-summit-south-africa-pinches-hard-for-fdi_686771.html</ref>

==Background==
A declaration at the end of [[2012 BRICS summit]] read that: "Brazil, Russia, India and China thank South Africa for the proposal to host the 5th summit in 2013. They intend to provide multifaceted support for it."<ReF>http://www.itar-tass.com/en/c154/378346.html</ref>

